column2: SELECT so.bestObjID, so.specObjID, so.ra, so.dec, nd.ra as Gal_ra, nd.dec as Gal_dec, so.plate, so.mjd, so.fiberID, gsl.oiii_#_flux, gsl.h_beta_flux, gsl.nii_#_flux, gsl.h_alpha_flux, so.z, so.snMedian_g, gsl.sii_#_flux, gsl.sii_#_flux, gsl.oi_#_flux into mydb.all_dwarfs_MPAJHU from MyDB.MyTable_# as nd CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (nd.ra, nd.dec, #) as w JOIN SpecObjAll so ON so.bestObjID = w.objID JOIN GalSpecLine as gsl ON so.specObjid = gsl.specObjid
